ed="T" n="0717c07"/><persName key="A000437">釋佛陀多羅</persName>，<name>華</name>言<persName key="A000437">覺救</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000055418">北天竺罽賓</placeName>人也。<lb
ed="T" n="0717c08"/>齎多羅夾<ptr type="glossary" target="#g302"/>，誓化<placeName key="PL000000000083"><anchor xml:id="beg0717sgsz6"/>支<anchor xml:id="end0717sgsz6"/>那</placeName>，止<placeName key="PL000000023663">洛陽白馬寺</placeName><ptr target="#n312"/>，譯出<lb
ed="T" n="0717c09"/>《大方廣圓覺了義經》<ptr target="#n313"/>。此經近譯，不委何年，且<lb
ed="T" n="0717c10"/>隆道為懷，務甄<ptr type="glossary" target="#g314"/>詐妄，但<ptr type="glossary" target="#g888"/>真詮不謬，豈假具<lb
ed="T" n="0717c11"/>知年月耶？<persName key="A000437">救</persName>之行迹，莫究其終。<date notBefore-iso="+0827-03-18" key="j20231922026427" notAfter-iso="+0836-01-25"><name>大和</name>中</date>，<placeName key="PL000000042639">圭<lb
ed="T" n="0717c12"/>峯</placeName><persName key="A000587">密<roleName>公</roleName></persName>著疏<ptr target="#n315"/>判解，經本一卷，後分二卷成<lb
ed="T" n="0717c13"/>部，續又為鈔，演暢幽邃。今<placeName key="PL000000023467">東京</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000003749">太原</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000034650">三蜀</placeName>盛<lb
ed="T" n="0717c14"/>行講演焉。</p>
